"*Zvali* su ga da dođe na sastanak." (They called him to come to the meeting.)

"Oni su mu *zvali* ime." (They called him by his name.)

"Mnogo ljudi je *zvalo* za pomoć." (Many people called for help.)

"Njihovi prijatelji su ih *zvali* da dođu." (Their friends called them to come.)

"Kada je pozvala, *zvala* je i njega." (When she called, she called him too.)